# Code Review Checklist (Frontend)

- [ ] Interactive elements are real controls (`button`, `a`, `input`) with accessible names
- [ ] Images have meaningful `alt` (or `alt=""` when decorative)
- [ ] Lists/maps have stable keys ({{#if isReact}}React{{/if}})
- [ ] No raw HTML injection without sanitization
- [ ] Loading / error / empty states for async UI
- [ ] Responsive layout verified at mobile + desktop widths
- [ ] New dependencies justified (size, maintenance, license)
- [ ] `{{lintCommand}}` and `{{testCommand}}` pass locally
